1000 matches completed in IPL

The Indian Premier League (IPL) has completed the journey of 1000 matches in 15 years. On Sunday, the historic 1000th match was played between the tournament&#39;s first champion Rajasthan Royals and 5-time champions Mumbai Indians at the Wankhede Stadium in Mumbai, which Mumbai won by hitting 3 consecutive sixes in the last over.

