Delhi lost the third match of the season: Rajasthan won by 57 runs

Delhi Capitals, playing in the absence of Rishabh Pant, have lost the third match in the current season of the Indian Premier League. The team was defeated by Rajasthan Royals by 57 runs. This is Rajasthan&#39;s overall 14th win over Delhi.

