Suyash Sharma: Who is KKR new mystery spinner Suyash Sharma?

After Sunil Narine and Varun Chakraborty, Kolkata Knight Riders have got another mystery spinner. The name of this mystery spinner is Suyesh Sharma. This 19-year-old bowler bowled some such mysterious balls in his very first IPL match that the RCB batsmen were stunned. In his debut match, Suyash took three wickets.
